{"tid":2090130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一日黃店一世都係黃店] 所有黃店已經被打壓 但請緊記","createTime":"2020-07-02T04:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T05:25:58.000Z","uid":41873,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d08a4b928a8d16a572ebd63275eb537928009676","tid":2090130,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:20:06.000Z","msg":"Pazu 薯伯伯<br />\nnmS1tSSpon mshoredr &middot; <br />\n強烈呼籲：拆除文宣<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆是最能體現 be water 哲學的場地，「撕一貼百」是策略，但「來去無影」也是策略。一開始時，連儂牆就沒有永恆的打算，只求大家毋忘過去，銘記心中。<br />\n<br />\n新一輪的打壓已然展開，我在這裡作出一個強烈的呼籲，此呼籲並非空穴來風，礙於實際情況，不宜公開因由。<br />\n<br />\n強烈呼籲：<br />\n<br />\n所有店鋪，即時拆除文宣。<br />\n<br />\n同路人，永記於心。<br />\n<br />\n（寫於 2020 年 7 月 2 日 11 時，《國安法》生效後 37 小時。）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要記低哂所有係今日前已經表哂態既黃店 我呢世就一蚊都唔會俾藍店賺 無黃店就返屋企自已煮 你吹得我漲？ 屌你老母</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"67d2217e97de43a2af5f763fc278d8a2fb96a140","tid":2090130,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bbd1adf5867c28b62bdde1e64a178b8b8cfdca6","tid":2090130,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:21:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d935854e9383101b5365e82aa486a77fa0860708","tid":2090130,"uid":207614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:21:24.000Z","msg":"藍店連儂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0350cd0405812d1474e573399f5009e6fa4208","tid":2090130,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:21:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f88114afc2a7f3cda3f2b4434066b23b8f60c0f5","tid":2090130,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:22:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2d9d0e13d3ce540a5f7f7024963c84c7a4960e6","tid":2090130,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{